        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "and fiery indignation",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] Lit., “and a jealousy of fire.” He is thinking of God “as a consuming fire” (",
        "children": []
